WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.026 --> 00:00:07.050
Good evening, family.

00:00:07.050 --> 00:00:08.811
Thank you for joining me again tonight.

00:00:08.811 --> 00:00:17.173
I got around a little later because we went to church, and I was rushing to feed the kids and stuff before, and I apologize.

00:00:18.027 --> 00:00:26.148
I want to get on here earlier because there are so many of you that say, "Hey, I go to bed.

00:00:26.148 --> 00:00:27.359
What?

00:00:27.359 --> 00:00:29.600
You're praying way too late, Brandon.

00:00:37.066 --> 00:00:37.479
" And I would love it.

00:00:39.439 --> 00:00:46.169
I think I'm trying to start to get the live streams around 7:00, but that'll affect going to Wednesday night church and stuff.

00:00:46.169 --> 00:00:49.840
I don't know what we're going to do.

00:00:52.080 --> 00:01:00.020
But I know in my heart when I do the live streams around 7:00, we'll get over 10,000 people on a live stream at one time.

00:01:13.190 --> 00:01:13.500
And so, I believe that's significant for prayer results.

00:01:13.500 --> 00:01:15.787
You know, we're touching the nations.

00:01:15.787 --> 00:01:20.440
I believe with all my heart we're touching the nations for Jesus.

00:01:34.920 --> 00:01:35.440
And people are getting saved, and it's just wonderful what God is doing here.

00:01:38.606 --> 00:01:43.849
So, I just want to be encouraging tonight about some of the things that the Lord was—we were praying over last night.

00:01:43.849 --> 00:02:02.936
Whenever the spirit of the Lord hit my little girl in that river as she was interceding for me, interceding with Diana, and they were praying, everybody kept saying, "I hear a third voice.

00:02:02.936 --> 00:02:09.253
" We don't know who the third voice was.

00:02:15.490 --> 00:02:15.820
I kept thinking it was Sister Billie.

00:02:25.300 --> 00:02:25.690
I told Diana I thought she was playing something and they were praying alongside it, but there was nobody else in the house.

00:02:25.690 --> 00:02:39.450
They were in the closet and they were praying, and it was so loud in the closet that it sounded like a third person was praying with them, but there was not a third person.

00:02:39.450 --> 00:02:45.360
So, I thought it was really interesting because I even personally thought there was a third person.

00:02:57.188 --> 00:02:57.599
And I kept thinking, and I told Diana, I said, "That sounds familiar.

00:02:57.599 --> 00:02:59.760
Who is that?

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:03.289
" And I was trying to figure it out myself.

00:03:03.289 --> 00:03:07.384
Diana said, "There was nobody in the closet with us.

00:03:07.384 --> 00:03:10.823
" So, we tried to think about that.

00:03:10.823 --> 00:03:14.183
We thought about that all the rest of the night.

00:03:14.183 --> 00:03:16.760
Who was the third voice praying and interceding?

00:03:16.760 --> 00:03:18.120
It was loud.

00:03:18.120 --> 00:03:24.239
But it was interesting because so many of you heard the third voice, too.

00:03:24.239 --> 00:03:25.1000
And Paisley was praying.

00:03:25.1000 --> 00:03:33.319
What we were praying about, we saw great revival coming to the nation, but it was with the youth.

00:03:48.266 --> 00:03:48.560
I saw a stirring in the youth that was all over Australia, all over America, Europe, but God was touching the young people in a glorious way.

00:03:50.839 --> 00:03:56.189
In a glorious way that was over the top of anything I could dare ask or think concerning the youth.

00:03:56.189 --> 00:04:04.400
The Lord said, "The devil has come after the youth hard, but I'm coming after him harder.

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:16.515
" Brandon, there will be—and I saw at the Church of His Presence, I saw a major youth revival also taking place with the glorious outpouring that's going to take place there.

00:04:21.626 --> 00:04:31.343
And then that was the same thing the Lord was talking to us about the youth building that the church in Collinsville is building and what God is going to do with the outpouring of the spirit on the youth in Oklahoma.

00:04:31.343 --> 00:04:41.759
I know in my heart, just as Paisley was praying and interceding for the youth and for me—I mean for the broadcast—it was just over the top because she was in that travail, as you know.

00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:48.800
And everybody asks, "How old is Paisley?

00:04:48.800 --> 00:04:51.400
" I don't let Paisley come on the internet.

00:04:51.400 --> 00:04:56.547
She's my youngest, and she is just—she's not even a teenager yet; she's just a child.

00:05:09.444 --> 00:05:09.842
And so, most people want to know—no, I've got a lot of creepy people that follow me, and I protect Paisley.

00:05:09.842 --> 00:05:20.765
There's a call on Paisley's life, and even with my other children as we all know, but Paisley is already seeing, and so we just don't talk about it.

00:05:20.765 --> 00:05:24.760
God's developing some things inside her, and it's through prayer.

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:37.657
I teach her everything I know; we pray in the car together, and I'm teaching her even before she becomes a teenager how to jump in these rivers and see prophetically and be yielded to it.

00:05:47.142 --> 00:05:47.474
And so, it's been amazing to watch what he's done with this little girl.

00:05:47.474 --> 00:05:52.639
Braden is very techy and very smart like his mama.

00:05:52.639 --> 00:05:58.159
Diana is very smart, and they are able to do things that I can't do.

00:06:04.759 --> 00:06:05.189
So, it's very interesting how we all flow together with our giftings.

00:06:05.189 --> 00:06:10.926
Diana's really smart with finances and things like that, and Braden's smart with technological things.

00:06:10.926 --> 00:06:24.116
Paisley is still trying to figure out what God's called her to do, but I see more of a prayer mantle on her than any kid usually at her age.

00:06:24.116 --> 00:06:25.909
I've never seen it before.

00:06:25.909 --> 00:06:28.830
And I'm not bragging because she's my kid.

00:06:28.830 --> 00:06:34.463
You know, you'll go, "Well, yeah, of course you'd say that because that's your child.

00:06:34.463 --> 00:06:36.639
" No, no, no.

00:06:36.639 --> 00:06:37.1000
This is different.

00:06:37.1000 --> 00:06:39.020
It's different.

00:06:39.020 --> 00:06:40.032
I know.

00:06:41.712 --> 00:06:43.200
And I'm one of those Simon Cowells.

00:06:43.200 --> 00:06:58.319
I'm not going to tell the person if their kid can't sing very well and they're in there auditioning for tryouts for singing, I'm going to say, "Honey, you just don't got it.

00:06:58.319 --> 00:06:59.039
It's okay.

00:06:59.039 --> 00:07:02.470
You can develop it or something through voice lessons.

00:07:14.309 --> 00:07:14.651
" I'm just really blunt.

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:26.355
And so, you know, that's why I believe that God's called me to go to certain places and rattle the places with the prophetic gifting inside of you.

00:07:26.355 --> 00:07:32.213
God calls you to stir churches; God calls you to stir the people.

00:07:38.213 --> 00:07:43.904
I have pastors from all around the world watch me and say, "Brandon, you're stirring us up to get us ready for the end times.

00:07:43.904 --> 00:07:47.880
" My job is to rattle the cages, to yell from there.

00:07:47.880 --> 00:08:03.120
And I don't ever feel like I'm correcting; I'm just yelling through what the Lord is telling me to say to pastors, to churches, to ministries to warn you that he's coming.

00:08:15.840 --> 00:08:16.080
And we must give altar calls.

00:08:16.080 --> 00:08:18.208
We must get the lost saved.

00:08:18.208 --> 00:08:27.119
Even if you don't think anybody in your congregation is going to be saved that night, give people the opportunity to make a choice.

00:08:29.999 --> 00:08:32.079
And God's going to hold us accountable for it.

00:08:34.737 --> 00:08:36.195
And I'm so thankful that we're seeing that now.

00:08:36.195 --> 00:08:38.779
We're seeing some fruit of that.

00:08:38.779 --> 00:08:47.223
We're seeing some fruit and some change, and we're seeing God move on some hearts.

00:08:49.760 --> 00:08:56.783
And it's wonderful to see the opportunity for the lost to give their heart to Jesus Christ.

00:08:56.783 --> 00:09:01.226
So, my heart is souls; my heart is a passion for souls.

00:09:01.226 --> 00:09:04.524
And we're seeing so many saved on this channel.

00:09:04.524 --> 00:09:10.832
It's amazing to see what the Lord is doing in these last days.

00:09:10.832 --> 00:09:14.355
Either we believe that he's coming or we don't.

00:09:14.355 --> 00:09:21.314
Either we believe that the coming of the Lord is at hand or we don't.

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:30.720
And if we do believe it, there'll be urgency behind what we say and how we act.

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:35.831
Some of us are growing more than others.

00:09:35.831 --> 00:09:44.377
Some of us are going through the birthing pains of ministry that we've never walked before.

00:09:54.040 --> 00:09:54.400
And that's me and Diana.

00:09:54.400 --> 00:09:56.258
We've never walked this before.

00:09:56.258 --> 00:10:17.520
So, we try to find camaraderie in people sometimes, and maybe the Lord always said for us to stay to ourselves and we need to grow with our birthing pains a little bit more privately.

00:10:17.520 --> 00:10:32.239
But I'm going to tell you this, it's all been amazing what the Lord has done with us in the last two and a half years.

00:10:32.879 --> 00:10:37.799
And the Lord spoke to me today and he told me to tell you this.

00:10:37.799 --> 00:11:08.251
We were driving down the road and I was going to do some things with Diana, and I'm telling you, I was looking over at a tree as I was driving and I was in the spirit praying, and all of a sudden the Lord said, "I want to talk to you about what's coming as you see this shot that President Trump has in his hand right now.

00:11:08.251 --> 00:11:08.480
" Do you see that?

00:11:08.480 --> 00:11:12.634
He's about to interject.

00:11:12.634 --> 00:11:16.733
He's about to administer into the economy.

00:11:16.733 --> 00:11:23.040
Is that what a doctor does?

00:11:23.040 --> 00:11:26.399
Yeah, inject into the economy.

00:11:26.399 --> 00:11:33.920
He's about to show up and show off in a way the Lord is in your finances.

00:11:35.291 --> 00:11:36.622
And he said, "There'll be many of you.

00:11:37.173 --> 00:11:39.299
" I want you to hear what he said.

00:11:39.299 --> 00:12:02.651
He said, "There'll be many of you that have had the opportunity and you have listened and obeyed what he's told you to do, and you over—just in a short amount of time—will have the wealth of what we talked about in Deuteronomy 8: wells you didn't dig, houses you didn't furnish, blessing and increase beyond anything you can ever comprehend, imagine, or think is coming to you.

00:12:04.297 --> 00:12:08.335
" And the Lord told me, 'Brandon, I'm telling you, I'm going to show you today.

00:12:08.335 --> 00:12:13.920
' As I was driving, he said, 'I'm going to show you today.

00:12:13.920 --> 00:12:27.839
I show you a lot of the warnings on the other side of the coin, but I am going to allow you to see the blessing side right now privately between me and you, and you can tell the people what's coming.

00:12:27.839 --> 00:12:32.390
' As I was looking over, I saw that big thing.

00:12:35.462 --> 00:12:44.240
I saw great financial stimulation coming to try to make a rally, to make things happy, to make people excited, and to pull people out of the funk of this 'sky is falling' mentality where everything is going to zero.

00:12:44.840 --> 00:12:46.263
The oil wells—everybody's freaking out—and war, war, war.

00:12:54.240 --> 00:12:59.325
I saw a stimulation coming where Trump had a battle plan of how to get the votes, since he is the president in November.

00:12:59.325 --> 00:13:02.136
I saw certain investments skyrocketing.

00:13:20.959 --> 00:13:21.439
I saw certain things starting to take off and the Lord said, 'This is...

00:13:21.439 --> 00:13:34.800
' I saw certain countries that have been dormant starting to come up, like Cuba and others, and I saw a blessing.

00:13:34.800 --> 00:13:37.209
People say, 'Well, Brandon, you said you saw the...

00:13:37.209 --> 00:13:38.912
' Yes, I see two sides.

00:13:50.780 --> 00:13:51.230
I see the fruit of stimulus; I see debt.

00:13:51.230 --> 00:13:57.260
I see what is happening to the American economy with a shot that only lasts for a little bit.

00:13:57.260 --> 00:13:58.844
It's like an adrenaline rush.

00:13:58.844 --> 00:14:09.920
Caffeine at Starbucks only lasts for a little bit, but it makes you feel good for probably two hours until you crash, but it still gets you through for that little time.

00:14:09.920 --> 00:14:13.1000
I saw certain rug pulls happening with great manipulation, like it was with silver.

00:14:13.1000 --> 00:14:17.980
What everybody said was not normal, what happened with silver.

00:14:17.980 --> 00:14:23.799
Remember it was way high and I told you?

00:14:23.799 --> 00:14:30.862
Everything I say on this is all in my opinion for your entertainment purposes only.

00:14:30.862 --> 00:14:32.880
I am not a financial adviser.

00:14:32.880 --> 00:14:37.215
I say all that because it's what I've been told to say.

00:14:37.215 --> 00:14:47.320
This is what our channel is about as the prophetic part of what I believe, but this is what I feel the Lord has told me and I'm entitled to my opinion.

00:14:48.356 --> 00:14:50.693
I believe this is what the Lord has told me.

00:14:50.951 --> 00:14:53.946
I could miss it; I could be off.

00:14:56.897 --> 00:14:57.306
I want to say, I saw...

00:15:10.514 --> 00:15:10.777
remember when I talked about silver?

00:15:10.777 --> 00:15:25.493
The Lord said, 'Today's a great day to sell silver,' and it was at a hundred and some dollars an ounce and then within just 24 hours it went down, but I wasn't allowed to talk about it.

00:15:29.759 --> 00:15:31.235
The Lord tells me things and he talks to me about investments.

00:15:31.235 --> 00:15:45.173
He tells me about property, he talks to me about all kinds of things and says, 'In the future, this will be worth this.

00:15:45.173 --> 00:15:52.160
' I'll just drive down the road and say, 'That right there is a good investment.

00:15:52.160 --> 00:16:01.805
' They are huge ideas, but I just pray over it.

00:16:01.805 --> 00:16:06.159
There are certain things that are coming.

00:16:15.960 --> 00:16:32.293
The Lord showed me about finances and the body of Christ, that there'll be rug pulls, great manipulation, and things to get you not to trust it—to trust banks and these other things—but then they'll try to get you to trust it.

00:16:32.293 --> 00:16:36.239
They don't want you to become really wealthy.

00:16:36.239 --> 00:16:43.307
I saw a manipulation where they don't want Bob, Joe, and Billy Bob to become extremely wealthy.

00:16:43.307 --> 00:16:54.160
So, if they're not smart enough to know when to hold them, know when to fold them, know when to walk away, and know when to run, you lose it all.

00:16:54.160 --> 00:17:03.768
And the Lord said, 'Count your money while you're sitting at the table.

00:17:03.768 --> 00:17:06.787
' I'm teasing; he didn't say that.

00:17:16.746 --> 00:17:17.280
I joke around with the Lord.

00:17:20.160 --> 00:17:23.239
The Lord has a great sense of humor.

00:17:40.009 --> 00:17:40.347
You all need to get to know him.

00:17:40.347 --> 00:17:44.773
Some of you do, but he has an amazing sense of humor.

00:17:55.440 --> 00:17:55.787
He made me, and so you have to go, 'If he can make me, he has a great sense of humor.

00:17:55.787 --> 00:18:00.679
' He likes to laugh and talk about sports.

00:18:00.679 --> 00:18:02.960
He likes to have fun.

00:18:02.960 --> 00:18:04.060
He loves his kids.

00:18:04.060 --> 00:18:13.067
Most people only see God as a religious fixture, like something too much to talk to or have a relationship with.

00:18:18.080 --> 00:18:19.333
But God is an ever-present help in a time of need.

00:18:19.333 --> 00:18:25.120
He loves you and he has a plan for your life.

00:18:25.120 --> 00:18:32.850
Most people only see him as someone you go to on Sunday or take communion and confess, then hope he forgives you.

00:18:32.850 --> 00:18:39.429
But I can assure you he does, and he has a plan for your life.

00:18:39.429 --> 00:18:44.987
I hear these things whenever he's talking to me about what's about to take place.

00:18:53.831 --> 00:18:54.133
I saw certain currencies going up in value.

00:18:54.737 --> 00:18:57.783
I saw a breakthrough in certain things.

00:19:08.720 --> 00:19:11.417
And he said, 'Remember I told you it wouldn't be as much as what people thought and they'll be disappointed in it, but it's a startup.

00:19:11.417 --> 00:19:18.280
' This is what you would call a startup if you listen to me.

00:19:32.187 --> 00:19:32.498
I saw Elon...

00:19:35.160 --> 00:19:38.114
I can say this because I saw Elon using something for X in the days ahead.

00:19:38.765 --> 00:19:44.240
I saw a lot of exchange and things about to take place even with Elon.

00:19:45.120 --> 00:19:56.753
I saw great, huge investments in certain cryptos from certain individuals like Michael Saylor and people like that who will dump billions into certain things in the days ahead.

00:19:56.753 --> 00:19:58.960
Hundreds of billions.

00:19:58.960 --> 00:20:00.240
Countries.

00:20:00.880 --> 00:20:07.657
I didn't see trillions; I saw hundreds of billions, and it was in certain countries and nations.

00:20:12.640 --> 00:20:14.826
I saw a frenzy that was coming in the future.

00:20:16.123 --> 00:20:22.320
I don't know when, but the Lord said specifically to pray for the summer months, to pray for this time frame with this shot.

00:20:22.320 --> 00:20:28.640
Praying for him to have wisdom on how to implement it.

00:20:34.640 --> 00:20:34.840
In my opinion, how will he implement this?

00:20:35.783 --> 00:20:45.013
I saw the man that takes over Jerome Powell's place trying to come up with a battle plan: 'How do we save America?

00:20:45.013 --> 00:20:50.690
How do we become what we need to be in these last days?

00:20:50.690 --> 00:20:53.800
' Basically, I don't know how else to say it.

00:20:53.800 --> 00:21:01.982
As I watched Putin, I saw a plan trying to take place concerning getting rid of Zelensky in the days ahead.

00:21:01.982 --> 00:21:03.540
'How do we eliminate Zelensky?

00:21:03.540 --> 00:21:05.554
How do we take him out?

00:21:05.554 --> 00:21:07.800
' Do you get what I'm saying?

00:21:07.800 --> 00:21:17.360
I saw the puppet Pinocchio with the big nose, Zelensky, who was being manipulated by Macron and the EU.

00:21:20.140 --> 00:21:23.413
He was a puppet, a marionette, and he was moving around.

00:21:23.413 --> 00:21:26.720
People say, 'Well, I like Zelensky.

00:21:26.720 --> 00:21:30.899
' You have to have more discernment.

00:21:33.120 --> 00:21:35.160
You have to come up higher in your prayer life.

00:21:35.160 --> 00:21:40.731
If you think these people are good, you are falsely mistaken.

00:21:40.731 --> 00:21:42.103
These people are not good.

00:21:42.103 --> 00:21:44.200
Am I saying Putin's good?

00:21:44.200 --> 00:21:46.213
No, he is not.

00:21:46.213 --> 00:21:47.369
They are all bad.

00:21:47.369 --> 00:21:57.462
But you can't let one go, 'Well, he's the good guy, he's the bad guy.

00:21:57.462 --> 00:22:03.013
' There are no good guys in politics.

00:22:03.013 --> 00:22:15.129
They may pretend they're good, but every one of them got there...

00:22:37.640 --> 00:22:37.840
you have to let the elevator go to the top.

00:22:37.840 --> 00:22:46.960
I'm telling you by the spirit of God what I've seen and the darkness in these nations in Europe.

00:22:46.960 --> 00:22:53.040
As the king was here—I don't know if he's still here or not—I told you he was a scorpion.

00:23:05.120 --> 00:23:15.760
And he came out with a scorpion and he turned towards Canada, he turned towards Europe, and he was getting ready to pinch his pincers.

00:23:15.760 --> 00:23:20.880
Then he comes here, has dinner, and does things.

00:23:43.511 --> 00:23:43.742
I told you I saw an antichrist darkness trying to overshadow our president.

00:23:44.436 --> 00:23:46.142
I didn't know that he was coming this week.

00:23:46.142 --> 00:23:54.260
That's when I saw it on Sunday and I said there's something very dark trying to come around Trump.

00:23:54.260 --> 00:23:55.580
What is this?

00:23:56.903 --> 00:23:57.234
I had no idea.

00:23:57.234 --> 00:23:58.559
It's the king.

00:23:58.559 --> 00:24:01.720
What is influencing Trump behind the scenes that we didn't know?

00:24:01.720 --> 00:24:05.303
What counsel was he being given from the king?

00:24:05.303 --> 00:24:17.668
Well, we're all trying to be friends and have fist bumps and eat pie and maybe some lemonade or whatever because we know Trump doesn't drink.

00:24:17.668 --> 00:24:25.884
But I saw an Antichrist spirit trying to be and I said, "What is this darkness, Lord?

00:24:34.129 --> 00:24:34.559
" And I couldn't get through it.

00:24:36.068 --> 00:24:37.143
And I thought, "What's going around Trump?

00:24:54.475 --> 00:24:55.513
" Then the king shows up.

00:25:03.792 --> 00:25:03.984
I said, "There's a darkness.

00:25:03.984 --> 00:25:06.411
" Now, am I saying the antichrist is the king?

00:25:06.411 --> 00:25:07.006
No.

00:25:20.480 --> 00:25:20.720
But there is a demonic covering over the royals that is dark.

00:25:21.902 --> 00:25:22.791
And I'm telling you, I've seen this—the lizard people.

00:25:22.791 --> 00:25:24.444
I've said there's darkness there.

00:25:33.235 --> 00:25:33.430
And I said there's part there like this is lineages of lizard stuff.

00:25:33.430 --> 00:25:42.808
And I saw certain royal families that have been keeping the bloodline clean.

00:25:47.110 --> 00:25:47.440
I saw darkness.

00:25:47.440 --> 00:25:49.840
Am I wrong?

00:25:53.200 --> 00:25:55.120
I don't know.

00:25:55.120 --> 00:25:59.773
So I just tell you what I saw.

00:25:59.773 --> 00:26:06.514
You said, "Well, Brandon, you're drinking some bad Kool-Aid.

00:26:06.514 --> 00:26:10.679
" Hey, I'm just telling you what I saw.

00:26:10.679 --> 00:26:13.484
And so when I saw him here, I thought that's what we saw.

00:26:13.484 --> 00:26:14.899
That's what the darkness was.

00:26:14.899 --> 00:26:26.359
Because I told Braden, I said, "What in the world was that?

00:26:27.899 --> 00:26:28.889
I haven't seen that darkness ever around Trump.

00:26:29.549 --> 00:26:32.880
What was over his shoulder talking to him?

00:26:44.240 --> 00:26:50.186
