' So, do you qualify for the blessing?

01:20:18.373 --> 01:20:18.676
Have you done what he's told you to do with what he's given you?

01:20:19.280 --> 01:20:22.311
Have you been willing to do it in your heart, or did you do it grudgingly?

01:20:28.766 --> 01:20:29.074
For God loves a cheerful giver.

01:20:37.463 --> 01:20:37.840
Your flesh might not like it when he first says it, but you do it willingly.

01:20:40.267 --> 01:20:40.613
You go, 'Okay, I'm getting willing.

01:20:49.211 --> 01:20:49.520
I'm getting obedient.

01:20:49.520 --> 01:20:57.017
' It's like he told me the other day when he wanted me to help Israel.

01:21:01.679 --> 01:21:01.1000
And he said, 'No.

01:21:05.180 --> 01:21:05.550
I told you to be willing and obedient.

01:21:05.550 --> 01:21:08.560
' I changed my attitude real fast.

01:21:13.378 --> 01:21:13.653
I want to make you happy.

01:21:13.653 --> 01:21:15.333
Let's make you happy, Lord.

01:21:18.384 --> 01:21:18.832
God loves a cheerful giver.

01:21:18.832 --> 01:21:20.180
What qualifies you for the blessing?

01:21:21.439 --> 01:21:25.999
You have to ask yourself that.

01:21:26.239 --> 01:21:30.293
I heard that by the spirit of God right then.

01:21:32.320 --> 01:21:34.350
I felt the anointing hit my ears.

01:21:54.719 --> 01:21:55.173
What qualifies you for the blessing?

01:22:04.639 --> 01:22:04.880
That's it.

01:22:04.880 --> 01:22:06.697
Take off that chokehold.

01:22:06.697 --> 01:22:10.160
Come up higher in your thinking.

01:22:10.160 --> 01:22:18.620
Many will talk as you walk the walk and you stay in sync with me.

01:22:18.620 --> 01:22:20.229
Hang on to me.

01:22:20.229 --> 01:22:24.960
I have greater days in store for you.

01:22:24.960 --> 01:22:27.440
Much more.

01:22:34.773 --> 01:22:40.240
In this day, a great day of overflow, and he wants to show exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask.

01:22:40.240 --> 01:22:41.520
Favor isn't fair.

01:22:41.520 --> 01:22:42.942
Favor, favor, favor.

01:22:42.942 --> 01:22:49.652
Instead of days of labor, labor, labor, days of heaven on earth.

01:22:49.652 --> 01:22:50.351
Favor, favor, favor.

01:22:56.800 --> 01:22:57.406
You either yield to it or you don't.

01:22:57.406 --> 01:23:02.360
Favor instead of labor, toil with your hands.

01:23:02.360 --> 01:23:06.560
But favor, days of favor, days of heaven on earth.

01:23:06.560 --> 01:23:26.526
He said, 'As long as you give me the glory for it.

01:23:26.526 --> 01:23:32.560
' As long as you keep the main thing, giving me the glory for it.

01:23:32.560 --> 01:23:37.031
Always give me praise with your mouth and give me glory for it.

01:23:37.031 --> 01:23:39.253
When they ask, 'Where did it come from?

01:23:39.253 --> 01:23:40.507
' Jesus provided for me.

01:23:43.600 --> 01:23:44.000
My Father has the cattle on a thousand hills.

01:23:44.000 --> 01:23:46.256
Keep the main thing the main thing.

01:23:46.256 --> 01:23:47.128
Don't exalt yourself.

01:23:47.128 --> 01:23:47.872
Exalt me.

01:23:47.872 --> 01:23:50.560
Give me praise for what I have given thee.

01:23:56.719 --> 01:23:56.999
And some of you will multiply exceedingly by threes.

01:24:09.149 --> 01:24:09.480
I saw the threes by tres.

01:24:09.480 --> 01:24:23.636
As you stay in sync with me each day, he'll tell you when to hold it and when to stop, when to go, when to flow, and where to sow and be strategic in where I tell you to sow.

01:24:23.636 --> 01:24:31.723
Give when I tell you to give.

01:24:31.723 --> 01:24:34.506
Be strategic in your giving.

01:24:34.506 --> 01:24:37.855
Be strategic in your giving.

01:24:37.855 --> 01:24:41.120
Give when I tell you to give.

01:24:44.480 --> 01:24:45.799
Don't give when you think you should give.

01:24:45.799 --> 01:24:56.018
Give when I tell you to give.

01:24:56.018 --> 01:25:01.259
Be led by My Spirit in your giving.

01:25:08.514 --> 01:25:13.759
For there's an anointing on the seed when you obey when I tell you to give out of emotion versus spirit-led giving.

01:25:13.759 --> 01:25:18.666
That's what He just said: be led by My Spirit.

01:25:24.040 --> 01:25:28.960
For those that are led by the Spirit of God are the sons and daughters of God.

01:25:33.059 --> 01:25:33.469
Right?

01:25:33.469 --> 01:25:35.520
So you see that.

01:25:40.547 --> 01:25:40.862
I see it right then.

01:25:40.862 --> 01:26:06.689
And when you see the canker, the devourer, the cankerworm, and the devourer eating those up around you and you're flourishing and your vineyards and your houses are full of godly treasure, you'll be able to share with those around you because it's been laid up for you.

01:26:24.639 --> 01:26:27.360
For great drought will come around those and you'll be that place, the man with the pitcher in his hand, as the Holy Spirit flows and ministers to them across the land, and the greater manifestations will flow out of compassion.

01:26:27.360 --> 01:26:40.250
It's laying hands on them to give the whole man spirit, soul, and body—healed in your emotions, healed in your body, healed and restored in your mind and your finances to be whole.

01:26:40.250 --> 01:26:43.060
It's not a prosperity gospel.

01:26:43.060 --> 01:26:46.251
That's why people say, "Well, it's prosperity gospel.

01:26:51.102 --> 01:26:51.404
" The Lord said, "No, it's not that.

01:26:51.404 --> 01:26:52.916
It's an obedience gospel.

01:27:01.165 --> 01:27:01.474
" The willing and obedient will eat the good of the land.

01:27:01.474 --> 01:27:15.189
Don't get jealous of someone's harvest; you don't know what they have sowed.

01:27:15.189 --> 01:27:21.325
For whatsoever a man sows, that will he also reap: good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over.

01:27:21.325 --> 01:27:23.972
Either you believe it or you don't.

01:27:23.972 --> 01:27:25.119
It's an obedience thing.

01:27:25.119 --> 01:27:29.679
Don't get mad at the reaping because it's just as much as sowing.

01:27:36.719 --> 01:27:37.279
You have to become good at sowing and reaping.

01:27:54.640 --> 01:27:54.880
If you're not good at reaping, you're not obeying the laws of seedtime and harvest.

01:27:59.271 --> 01:27:59.520
You sow, you reap.

01:28:04.103 --> 01:28:05.474
You don't sow and just let it die.

01:28:05.474 --> 01:28:08.930
There is a return and significant return by multiplication.

01:28:08.930 --> 01:28:14.936
Don't worry about what they say if they want to be in the crowd.

01:28:14.936 --> 01:28:16.719
Soon they will be free.

01:28:16.719 --> 01:28:18.000
It's time to expect the unexpected.

01:28:18.000 --> 01:28:21.908
What would be unexpected?

01:28:21.908 --> 01:28:22.616
Stretch.

01:28:22.616 --> 01:28:23.325
Stretch.

01:28:23.325 --> 01:28:27.880
Believe in Him for more expiration dates.

01:28:30.650 --> 01:28:31.520
I love that.

01:28:31.520 --> 01:28:35.760
"If ye be willing and obedient, ye shall eat the good of the land.

01:28:35.760 --> 01:28:45.004
But if ye refuse and rebel, ye shall be devoured with the sword," for the mouth of the Lord has spoken it.

01:28:45.004 --> 01:28:46.940
Thank You, Lord, for the obedient.

01:28:46.940 --> 01:28:54.229
We pray and obey what the Spirit of the Lord has told us to do today.

01:28:54.229 --> 01:28:55.853
We pray and obey.

01:28:55.853 --> 01:29:02.009
And we thank You, Lord, that the devourer has been rebuked.

01:29:02.009 --> 01:29:04.200
And the greater things will we do.

01:29:04.200 --> 01:29:05.040
Thank You, Father.

01:29:05.040 --> 01:29:08.640
Thank You, Jesus.

01:29:08.640 --> 01:29:10.679
It's time for the greater overflow.

01:29:10.679 --> 01:29:33.120
Oh, Father, we thank You, Lord, for creative ideas of how to get the wealth—creative ideas of how to get it out of the world's hands into the economic hands of the church, to pay off the churches, to give missionaries stuff that they need to be able to do everything by sowing a seed.

01:29:33.120 --> 01:29:39.005
Oh Father, I thank You, Lord, that we lack no good thing.

01:29:39.005 --> 01:29:47.778
Angels of the Lord—angels, aid and assistance—we send you out right now.

01:29:47.778 --> 01:29:50.770
Go, ministering spirits, and cause it to come forth.

01:29:50.770 --> 01:29:56.709
Supernatural increase in the name of Jesus.

01:30:27.040 --> 01:30:27.547
We yield to that.

01:30:27.547 --> 01:30:41.960
We yield to the blessing on our households, that we have jobs and better jobs.

01:30:41.960 --> 01:30:48.914
Father, they'll be promoted this week; their boss is going to come in and say, "Listen, you've been a good, diligent employee.

01:30:48.914 --> 01:30:51.485
We're going to give you a raise.

01:30:51.485 --> 01:30:53.875
Nobody else got a raise, but you will.

01:30:53.875 --> 01:30:58.320
" Well, if you don't believe that God will, then that's where you are.

01:30:58.320 --> 01:30:59.691
But why not you?

01:30:59.691 --> 01:31:07.520
Why not you and why not now to be the shift manager or the manager or the VP or the district manager?

01:31:24.200 --> 01:31:24.370
You could be the district manager of whatever company, and they call you tomorrow and say, "Listen, we don't know why we're doing this, but we know that you have the qualifications.

01:31:24.370 --> 01:31:30.680
We just overlooked you, but all of a sudden we want to bless you.

01:31:34.514 --> 01:31:36.880
" Why not you?

01:31:36.880 --> 01:31:40.853
Instead of being just the teacher of the school, you're the principal.

01:31:40.853 --> 01:31:43.110
Thank You, Father, for You are our exceedingly great reward.

01:31:43.110 --> 01:31:43.859
You're our abundant supply.

01:31:45.117 --> 01:31:48.950
You are able to do it.

01:32:00.329 --> 01:32:00.639
I am fully persuaded that the stimulus is coming.

01:32:00.639 --> 01:32:05.600
Father, I thank You, Lord, that President Trump—we're not looking to him; we're looking to You.

01:32:05.600 --> 01:32:15.880
But we thank You, Lord, that we are not a part of the economic system; we're part of Your system.

01:32:22.639 --> 01:32:23.026
And we believe, Father, for the certain things that You showed us.

01:32:23.026 --> 01:32:28.230
Father, I thank You, Lord, that the wealth of the sinner is laid up for the righteous.

01:32:28.230 --> 01:32:36.000
Oh God, we give You praise and glory.

01:32:36.000 --> 01:32:40.208
Healing in their bodies, healing in their minds, Father, that their marriages are restored.

01:32:40.208 --> 01:32:47.929
We call their marriages better than they've ever been.

01:32:47.929 --> 01:32:52.107
Their marriages have good love lives.

01:32:52.107 --> 01:32:53.138
They're friends.

01:32:53.138 --> 01:32:55.440
They're not struggling in their marriage.

01:32:55.440 --> 01:32:57.181
They have compassion for one another.

01:32:57.181 --> 01:32:58.297
They're not always bickering.

01:32:58.297 --> 01:33:01.005
Father, we call good marriages, godly marriages in this right now.

01:33:01.005 --> 01:33:03.760
We thank You, Lord, that You're stirring those old flames of love.

01:33:03.760 --> 01:33:05.720
Nobody is going to get a divorce.

01:33:05.720 --> 01:33:08.100
Nobody's going to get separated.

01:33:08.100 --> 01:33:10.790
They are going to stay together and they're going to get along.

01:33:10.790 --> 01:33:12.159
We're agreeing with you.

01:33:12.159 --> 01:33:14.824
Life and death is in the power of your tongue.

01:33:14.824 --> 01:33:23.337
So, Father, we lift up their marriages right now.

01:33:23.337 --> 01:33:30.880
We say repent of the word curses you have been speaking out of your mouth.

01:33:30.880 --> 01:33:34.666
Stop saying bad things over your marriage.

01:33:34.666 --> 01:33:38.640
Say it: "I repent for saying bad things about my marriage.

01:33:38.640 --> 01:33:39.760
My wife is wonderful.

01:33:39.760 --> 01:33:40.900
My husband is wonderful.

01:33:40.900 --> 01:33:42.260
We'll get along.

01:33:49.639 --> 01:33:49.889
We love each other.

01:33:49.889 --> 01:33:53.360
Our love life is better than it's ever been.

01:33:53.360 --> 01:33:57.679
We're going to stay together until the day we die.

01:33:57.679 --> 01:34:00.800
We're not going to get divorced.

01:34:00.800 --> 01:34:03.859
" You've got to speak life out of your mouth.

01:34:03.859 --> 01:34:08.604
Well, you don't know who I'm living with, Brandon.

01:34:12.514 --> 01:34:13.509
I'm telling you, she had to deal with a lot with me.

01:34:13.509 --> 01:34:14.871
I've been a rascal.

01:34:14.871 --> 01:34:17.120
I've not always been the nice guy.

01:34:17.120 --> 01:34:18.800
But I'm telling you, I love you, Dino.

01:34:33.853 --> 01:34:34.267
You ask my kids; back when Megan was first diagnosed, Braden knew it was hard, but we chose to fight it together and to fight it through.

01:34:37.154 --> 01:34:40.502
I said, "I'm not giving up on you and you're not giving up on me.

01:34:40.502 --> 01:34:42.304
We're making this work.

01:35:07.280 --> 01:35:07.519
" The statistics were 75% of all marriages get a divorce with a child with autism.

01:35:12.960 --> 01:35:13.373
And I said, "I'm beating the odds.

01:35:13.373 --> 01:35:15.027
I'm beating statistics.

01:35:18.560 --> 01:35:19.184
" And it was rough.

01:35:19.184 --> 01:35:26.503
But now I look at it and I don't think it was rough anymore.

01:35:31.406 --> 01:35:31.737
Now I go, "Whatever.

01:35:35.820 --> 01:35:36.600
" I used to be such a Type A personality, and I'm breaking out of that.

01:35:48.715 --> 01:36:04.550
The Lord will melt you and help you and cultivate love, and you get through things and you say, "Listen, we have our differences, but I love her more than I've ever loved her before.

01:36:04.560 --> 01:36:08.656
" We talk about it all the time.

01:36:14.369 --> 01:36:16.320
I say, "I don't know how I could love anybody more than I love you, and vice versa.

01:36:16.320 --> 01:36:29.897
" I'm not trying to make you blush, but it's the truth.

01:36:30.194 --> 01:36:33.386
You need to speak life over your marriage.

01:36:35.600 --> 01:36:36.053
You have to speak life.

01:36:36.053 --> 01:36:42.800
No one else is going to do it.

01:36:42.800 --> 01:36:46.743
No one else really cares.

01:36:46.743 --> 01:36:58.160
Either you want to fight for something or you don't.

01:36:58.160 --> 01:37:00.666
Say, "I repent for saying bad things.

01:37:16.792 --> 01:37:17.056
I may say something stupid out of my mouth sometimes.

01:37:17.056 --> 01:37:19.741
Oh God, I call crop failure over that.

01:37:19.741 --> 01:37:20.568
Forgive me.

01:37:52.251 --> 01:37:52.663
I shouldn't say stupid stuff.

01:37:52.663 --> 01:38:01.360
" When you get mad and say something stupid, repent and walk in love with your marriage, right?

01:38:12.960 --> 01:38:14.397
And that's the same thing with your kids.

01:38:14.397 --> 01:38:19.233
Bless your children.

01:38:19.233 --> 01:38:21.291
They're not good-for-nothings.

01:38:21.291 --> 01:38:23.120
They're not lazy.

01:38:23.120 --> 01:38:24.719
They're not angry.

01:38:24.719 --> 01:38:30.635
They're not rebellious.

01:38:30.635 --> 01:38:41.460
I don't ever speak word curses over my kids.

01:38:51.474 --> 01:38:51.760
You speak blessings over them.

01:38:51.760 --> 01:39:00.570
"Oh Father, I thank you, Lord, that we are training these children up in the way they should go, and when they get older, they'll not depart from it.

01:39:13.520 --> 01:39:19.382
" I believe, God, that you have a hand on my children, and that they are filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost, and every tongue that rises against them will be condemned.

01:39:32.986 --> 01:39:37.800
I will not stand for it.

01:39:37.800 --> 01:39:40.080
We plead the blood of Jesus.

01:39:40.080 --> 01:39:51.909
No weapon formed against them will prosper.

01:40:21.559 --> 01:40:21.899
And I don't let them just hang out with just anybody.

01:40:22.879 --> 01:40:24.823
And it's just the way it is.

01:40:24.823 --> 01:40:29.920
We don't let our kids go and hang out with certain things.

01:40:29.920 --> 01:40:32.320
We just don't do it.

01:40:32.320 --> 01:40:33.140
Period.

01:40:46.300 --> 01:40:46.670
I don't know what you're doing behind closed doors.

01:40:46.670 --> 01:41:10.200
People have a church face, and it's all holy in church, and then when they get in the car, it's a totally different person.

01:41:12.760 --> 01:41:13.499
You don't know who they are behind there.

01:41:45.360 --> 01:41:46.209
And I don't have time to try to discern and pray for everybody to make sure my kids are going into a wolf's lair—a safe environment?

01:41:55.040 --> 01:41:55.369
You don't know if the guy's a pedophile or she's a pedophile.

01:42:05.749 --> 01:42:06.183
You don't know.

01:42:17.940 --> 01:42:18.210
And nowadays, I'm like, "No, we're good.

01:42:18.210 --> 01:42:32.960
" Until I get a download from the Holy Ghost, you aren't going around anybody until I know, because we don't know who they really are behind the doors of their own home.

01:42:32.960 --> 01:42:34.160
We just don't do that.

01:42:34.160 --> 01:42:36.587
They're my treasure.

01:42:36.587 --> 01:42:42.016
Watch who your kids hang around.

01:42:50.491 --> 01:42:50.937
It's so important you protect the gift inside of them.

01:43:26.480 --> 01:43:26.743
We don't let anybody around our kids.

01:43:26.743 --> 01:43:27.531
We don't.

01:43:27.531 --> 01:43:28.057
Period.

01:43:45.119 --> 01:43:45.429
"I don't know who you are.

01:43:45.429 --> 01:43:48.286
We want to do this with them.

01:43:48.286 --> 01:43:49.657
" "No, I'm sorry.

01:43:49.657 --> 01:43:53.787
" Or I just ignore you if you ask too many times.

01:43:54.036 --> 01:43:55.031
I don't want it.

01:43:55.031 --> 01:43:55.580
No.

01:43:55.580 --> 01:43:56.779
Leave me alone.

01:43:56.779 --> 01:44:04.037
Does that make sense?

01:44:28.869 --> 01:44:37.800
And you've got to protect the treasure that's inside of them.

01:44:37.800 --> 01:44:57.139
"Well, they mean well.

01:44:57.139 --> 01:45:06.639
" I don't care.

01:45:30.000 --> 01:45:30.549
I don't know you.

01:45:30.549 --> 01:45:53.040
I'm not responsible for your feelings; I'm responsible for what I'm responsible for.

01:46:00.537 --> 01:46:09.112
And when I went up there and got that shot, I still hold it very strong: I should have never done that.

01:46:12.079 --> 01:46:23.733
I take full responsibility for giving the vaccination to my daughter.

01:46:23.733 --> 01:46:39.560
But I refuse to not be prayed up ever again and let those things happen.

01:46:39.560 --> 01:46:51.383
I said, "Listen, I take full responsibility because I see my daughter still overcoming at 21 years old," sitting in her room and overcoming what she's still overcoming.

01:46:51.383 --> 01:47:04.390
Yes, she's come a long way, and we give God all the glory for that.

01:47:17.679 --> 01:47:17.839
But it was my choice.

01:47:18.479 --> 01:47:19.576
It wasn't Megan; she couldn't speak for herself.

01:47:24.430 --> 01:47:24.820
"I don't want that shot, Daddy.

01:47:24.820 --> 01:47:40.460
" I take full responsibility for it.

01:47:46.069 --> 01:47:48.410
And she's still living my decision as a father to give her the flu vaccination.

01:47:48.410 --> 01:47:55.480
And in the natural, I'm believing God for her healing.

01:47:55.480 --> 01:47:59.360
And I believe that the Lord has healed her.

01:48:24.378 --> 01:48:30.080
But until you live it, you can't say anything to it.

01:49:13.474 --> 01:49:14.011
And it's a hard pill to swallow at 21 years old.

01:49:37.520 --> 01:49:37.893
You see her, and my niece and everybody, they're all getting married, and my daughter's still lying in her bed.

01:49:39.599 --> 01:49:42.023
And you look at it and go, "Man, life goes on.

01:49:42.023 --> 01:49:55.440
" She's graduating college—my niece is a couple weeks younger than my daughter—and she's getting married in the next couple weeks.

01:49:55.440 --> 01:50:17.189
That's a hard pill to swallow.

01:50:17.199 --> 01:51:15.413
When you look at your daughter and we still have to bathe her, and you have to get her dressed every day and make sure she's clean and sanitary, and you've got family that are getting married and going off, and you still have a child lying in the bed, and you go, "That was my choice.

01:51:19.132 --> 01:51:31.430
" And that's like I said—I, and people go, "Why are you the way you are?

01:51:31.440 --> 01:51:36.231
" I'm very intense about a lot of things because I've been through hell.

01:51:40.880 --> 01:51:42.639
And people will never get it until you've walked through the valley of hell.

01:51:47.360 --> 01:52:08.239
And I'm trying to help you to speak good things out of your mouth towards your kids and bless them.

01:52:08.239 --> 01:52:20.100
Bless them.

01:52:20.100 --> 01:52:31.451
There's always some "Sister Clipboard" or some preacher behind the pulpit telling you there's sin in your life or whatever happened, when they don't know.

01:52:31.451 --> 01:52:37.680
When you walk through the valley, there's no sin.

01:52:37.680 --> 01:52:40.150
It's clean—as clean as the blood.

01:52:40.729 --> 01:52:42.013
The blood washes me clean.

